       LineEnding +
       'replenish it manually once in a while.' +

       LineEnding + LineEnding +
       'Your house layout must look exactly like the image to the right!' +
       LineEnding +
       'Looking close enough won''t do, it has to look exactly the same.' +
       LineEnding +
       'If you have more rooms, move them 3 squares away so they are never,' +
       LineEnding +
